Detailed Description

DEI context buffers needed for deinterlacing operation.

struct Vps_DeiCtxBuf

Field Documentation

UInt32 Vps_DeiCtxBuf::chNum

Channel number to which the DEI context buffers be given. If only one channel is supported, then this should be set to 0.

void* Vps_DeiCtxBuf::fldBuf[VPS_DEI_MAX_CTX_FLD_BUF]

Array of DEI context field buffer pointers. This is not applicable for platform TI814X. Please refer the user guide for TI814X, that came with this release.

void* Vps_DeiCtxBuf::mvBuf[VPS_DEI_MAX_CTX_MV_BUF]

Array of DEI context MV buffer pointers.

void* Vps_DeiCtxBuf::mvstmBuf[VPS_DEI_MAX_CTX_MVSTM_BUF]

Array of DEI context MVSTM buffer pointers. This is not applicable for platform TI814X. Please refer the user guide for TI814X, that came with this release.
